+| `.claude/settings.json` | `58310089dbf8e19e…` | `5c05eeb12eefb37d…` |
+| `scripts/hooks/MANIFEST.sha256` (sha do próprio manifesto) | `3f0285089357880f…` | `3f0285089357880f…` |
